FBIS4-7491 "dreeu063_p_94008" FBIS-EEU-94-063 Daily Report 31 Mar 1994 POLAND Radio, TV Broadcasting Council Head Appointed Radio, TV Broadcasting Council Head Appointed LD3103143294 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1300 GMT 31 Mar 94 LD3103143294 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network Polish BFN [Excerpt] Ryszard Bender, hitherto a member of the National Radio and Television Broadcasting Council, was today appointed chairman of the council by the president. Ryszard Bender told journalists that he does not envisage any changes in the policy of the council regarding the granting of broadcasting concessions. [passage omitted]
